 Receiver communication # Obtain data from receiver # After you get the service (refer to SDK Initialization), you can use the requestReceiverListener method of the service to monitor the receiver data. The requestReceiverListener requires you to pass in the IReceiverListener.Stub object. You can inherit the object, implement the relevant interface, and obtain the required data through the implementation of the interface. Some callback interfaces call back at a certain frequency (such as location information and satellite information), and some interfaces require a command to the receiver (refer to Send data to the receiver) before calling back.
